parent.description: Required. The repository in which to list workflow configs. Must be in the format `projects/*/locations/*/repositories/*`.

pageSize.description: Optional. Maximum number of workflow configs to return. The server may return fewer items than requested. If unspecified, the server will pick an appropriate default.

pageToken.description: Optional. Page token received from a previous `ListWorkflowConfigs` call. Provide this to retrieve the subsequent page. When paginating, all other parameters provided to `ListWorkflowConfigs` must match the call that provided the page token.
